headline: 'Lowest-probability outcome': Netflix's $72 billion deal for Warner Bros. Discovery stuns Wall Street
summary: Netflix’s $72 billion takeover of Warner Bros.’ studios and streaming assets stunned Wall Street and immediately ignited a high-stakes antitrust fight.

headline: What is Netflix buying? A visual history of 100 years of Warner Bros.
summary: Netflix announced Friday that it has agreed to acquire Warner Bros. Discovery’s studio streaming-focused company HBO Max for $82.7 billion, including debt.
